E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1128','285','周艳、彭习斌、李涛','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>日，嘉鱼县畜牧兽医局&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组来到潘家湾镇东村村，实地勘察该村急需整修的塘堰、泵站及沟渠，商讨冬季农田水利建设方案。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">潘家湾镇东村村地处我县最北段，地势低洼，每年抗洪排涝任务十分艰巨。由于缺政策、缺资金、缺技术，泵站失修、沟渠淤积，严重影响了该村四千余村民正常的农业生产生活。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">得知这些情况后，县畜牧兽医局急该村群众之所急，克服机关经费紧张的困难，及时筹措<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>万元资金支持该村清挖塘堰、维修泵站等农田水利设施建设，深入开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据了解，潘家湾镇东村村需要清淤老塘堰<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>处，清淤面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>万平方米，维修小泵站<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>座。工程已于昨日开工，计划本月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>日前完工。通过践行县委、县政府&ldquo;兴水利、促发展、惠民生&rdquo; 的主题活动，大力开展冬季农田水利设施建设，力争为明年春季农业生产的顺利开展提供保障。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1129','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-12/dbe8d9313fe1b42ac96491994cc253ee.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><br />\r\n在杭瑞陶瓷参观<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>日，县委书记熊征宇，县长余珂率我县党政代表团赴通城县参观学习。在家的县四大家领导参加活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">代表团一行先后来到通城县杭瑞陶瓷、瀛通电子等企业和银山广场进行了参观。瀛通电子有限公司是该县在外创业人士投资创办的，主要生产耳机及耳机线、电脑电话连接线、音频线等。总投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.5</span>亿元，安排就业<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>人，是该县&ldquo;回归工程&rdquo;中固定资产投资最大的企业和电子信息材料产业龙头企业。嘉鱼党政代表团参观了该企业的生产车间、办公楼后，深受启发，表示嘉鱼县在招商引资工作方面，也要多联系在外企业家，招引大型、优质的&ldquo;回归&rdquo;企业。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇表示，通城县新一届领导班子到位后，工作干劲很足，使该县各项工作都取得了很好开局，我县四大家班子要学习他们这种扎实的工作作风。他说，近年来通城与嘉鱼两地来往密切，干部交流频繁，形成了良好的互动关系，希望今后两地继续加强交流，互相学习，共同发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">通城县委书记姜卫东、县长来华雄对我县党政代表团的到来表示了欢迎，并陪同参观。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1130','285','黄念','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">&ldquo;王师傅，麻烦你把这边的淤泥清理干净，然后再挖深点。&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>日，在渡普镇王庄村三组，组长张青平正在指挥着挖掘机为塘堰清淤。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据张青平介绍，这口塘名叫合海张塘，面积七亩，是三组重要的农业灌溉用水来源。但是因为常年疏于管理，如今塘里积累了厚厚的淤泥，今年上半年的干旱使得这口塘近乎干涸，很难充分发挥灌溉效益。&ldquo;像这样的塘堰村里还有许多，这次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，给了村里整修塘堰的机会，才决定整修这口塘。&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据悉，渡普镇党委政府召开专题会议，成立了水利建设领导小组和工作专班，广泛征求意见，采取因地制宜、急事急办、量力而行的原则制定工作方案。全镇确定了急需解决的水利工程项目共<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>大项，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">42</span>小项。其中，塘堰整修<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>处、沟渠清淤<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">22</span>处、泵站维修<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>处、涵闸整修<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>处、桥梁兴修<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>处，并确保<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月底全面完工。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">利用当前晴好天气，该镇各村水利建设进展迅速，其中，渡普口村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>个组完成沟渠清淤<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"19000\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19000</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>、蒲圻湖村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>个组完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13000</span>米、东湖村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>个组完成<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"18000\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18000</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>；净堡村四组顾家门口塘已全面完工，王庄村三组合海张塘基本完工，大路村十组担丘塘及烟墩村六组蔡许塘也已全面启动。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1131','285','熊铁山、谢翔','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>日上午，随着大型挖掘机的隆隆声，县财政局驻官桥镇两湖村三万工作队的塘堰整治工程正式动工，附近不少村民也自发带来了锄头、篓子，投入到清淤大军当中，现场一片热火朝天。&ldquo;这次政府为我们做的是好事、实事儿，我们非常支持，我们也不能落后&rdquo;。村民胡海一边清淤一边对记者说。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据了解，两湖村有八口塘堰需要整治。这些塘污泥淤塞严重，浅窄渗水，蓄水功能衰退。一遇到干旱，塘里几乎完全干涸，村里数千亩农田无法灌溉，严重影响群众生产生活。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">截止目前，该村塘堰整治已动工<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>口，整治面积达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12600</span>立方米，石方量达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">130</span>立方米；已组织劳力<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>余人，投入资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50000</span>余元。整个工程竣工后，预计可以解决附近<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">860</span>余亩农田灌溉问题，使周边<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">130</span>余户农户的生产生活得到保障。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1132','285','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-12/7b8596bcbb59f2d7a59ca5b26d84f865.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">沟渠清淤现场</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" day=\\\\\"12\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，记者在潘家湾镇肖家洲村、四邑村、东村村等多处沟渠整治现场看到，挖掘机挥舞长臂掘土清淤，驻村&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组和镇村干部群众一道，挥锄抖土、挥汗如雨，处处一片繁忙的劳动景象。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据该镇镇长涂秋意介绍，自&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动开展以来，该镇组织专班调查摸底，确定项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">83</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，其中沟渠清淤</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">65</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个、泵站维修</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个、塘堰清淤</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，其他沟渠硬化、建闸等项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个。全部项目拟定于元旦前完工。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">截至目前，全镇已到位资金</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">183.5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，其中省&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组支持</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，县农行、住建局、卫生局、畜牧局等单位&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组共出资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">22.5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，镇政府投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">79</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，村组自筹资金</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">62</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元。目前全镇共开工水利建设项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">72</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">处，已竣工</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">28</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">处，未开工项目计划在一周内全面开工。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-12/5ccde6930a556ced9ad365c2676c0318.jpg\\\\\" /></font></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><br />\r\n</font><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">干群齐心疏通沟渠</font></span></o:p></span></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
